            <h3 class="frontpage">Energy</h3>
            <br>
            <p>We provide strategic planning and related implementation services to help energy enterprises define goals, manage risks, meet financial expectations, manage regulatory challenges, and achieve competitive advantage and market leadership.  Being located in Houston, Texas we have worked with most major oil companies in every business area.  From wellhead to burner tip including extensive experience in Energy Trading systems.</p>
