            <h3 class="frontpage">Healthcare</h3>
            <br>
            <p>Our understanding of the complexity of today's information technology and how it relates to the healthcare industry positions us to assist clients in various IT resource needs including HIPAA compliance support.  The implementation of new systems is bringing new challenges and the need for talent to assist overloaded IT staffs has never been higher. <br>
