            <h3 class="frontpage">Services</h3>
            <br>
            <p>Having been in the Services business ourselves and helping other Engineering and Consulting firms with their internal backoffice and project tracking needs we know the issues that arise.  Something as simple as a saleperson commission plan can become a nightmare of a spreadsheet in many cases.  Let us clean up that spreadsheet and maybe provide a few shortcuts for your business.<br>
